commit.message: Files match current master
Fixed frontend
Client intermediary
Added app routes and processing for them
Front end works
Cleaned up the api file.
Now instead of returning the full json object, getBlockNumber just returns the number
Blocknumber has now been successfully tested
Fixed the getBlockNumber function

Merge branch 'lib' of https://github.com/wadeAlexC/ethsingapore into lib

Merge necessary to fix dependencies
The helper functions changeTopic and getBlockNumber in api.js now return lexical closures so that they can access the node object.
Merge branch 'lib' of https://github.com/wadeAlexC/ethsingapore into lib
Added the express and data-store npm packages.
Frontend
The changeTopic function now changes the local variable topic

The message handler that is being used to listen to pubsub topics now checks to see that the sender of the message is the authority. Additionally, an endpoint to the internal api was added that allows this authority hash to be changed.
Implemented the basic API for the client. It has not been tested except for a run to make sure that there are not any syntax errors
intermediate
added express
Fixed a dependency issue in lib.js
Added a node creation step to the lib.js file
Added callbacks to lib to make the behavior of the skeleton more predictable.
Created skeleton module for the library functions
Created the directory structure
Added package.json
Initial commit
